{"type": "article", "id": 25071, "title": "极简风格储物柜", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-07T07:10:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132616w13eTqnGi65Ct7af.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是荷兰设计师 Rik ten Velden 新推出的储物柜，外形方正且简洁干净。抽屉本身并没有凹槽，只通过抽屉之间的横竖细长线条来区分不同的板块，方形的柜子外面外面增加了黑色金属框架，以强调了这种线条感。柜子本身带有可插入电线的缺口，可以用来连接键盘或者电脑。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132613tqU8kSBlsOpIecQa.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132613SLDyWNcaqkRbX5ro.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132614GhuVXQlybrKU3S4P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132614JTflFIjZGxu7Vstc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132615P1sdaEirLVuDJWeA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}